pattern matching

* basically an if/else-if or switch/case code block on steroids
* practical use-cases
    + easier to read code
    + guarantee exhaustive matching for all possible e.g. enum variants
    + unpacking optional values

Python
* planned for Python 3.10 (status October 2020)
* PEP 622 - Structural Pattern Matching

Rust
* part of the language since the start
